    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Not overwriting, just shadowing.\r\n\r\nCurrently this is allowed:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfoo: uint256\r\n\r\n@external\r\ndef bar():\r\n    foo: bool = True\r\n```\r\n\r\nbut this raises with a `NamespaceCollision`:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfoo: uint256\r\n\r\n@external\r\ndef bar(foo: bool):\r\n    pass\r\n```",
